<plot>The evil Garaden Army has decided to attack Primus Star, home of Princess Millian. It seems that a princess known as Princess Millian has stolen a secret data disk from the clutches of an evil empire, and she safely smuggles out the information through a robot by the name of Pibot, but is captured herself. Bomberman is training in his headquarters when news arrives about that Princess Millian has been captured! The Empire claims back the disks to rebuild Bagular, but a mysterious villain was controlling him from Planet Gossick. It is Evil Bomber, exacting revenge! Bomberman is ready for action! And it's up to him to save the beautiful Princess Millian, defeat Bagular, then destroy Garaden and defeat Evil Bomber at all costs!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?078438</url></doc>
